### Variables
@baseUrl = https://qjfygjtondljywhbqbfj.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Récupérer tous les invités (cas nominal)
GET {{baseUrl}}/guests-get-guest-list?event_id=event-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 2 - Filtrer par statut RSVP
GET {{baseUrl}}/guests-get-guest-list?event_id=event-uuid-here&rsvp_status=accepted
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 3 - Filtrer par catégorie
GET {{baseUrl}}/guests-get-guest-list?event_id=event-uuid-here&category=family
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 4 - Combinaison de filtres
GET {{baseUrl}}/guests-get-guest-list?event_id=event-uuid-here&rsvp_status=accepted&category=friend
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 5 - Erreur: event_id manquant
GET {{baseUrl}}/guests-get-guest-list
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

